title: Carroll County Arts Council to screen silent Halloween film 'The Phantom Carriage'
text:
Published By: Carroll County Times - Today 
The Carroll County Arts Council will host a screening of the classic silent film "The Phantom Carriage" on Friday at the Carroll Arts Center...
